016package org.lifstools.jgoslin.parser;
017
018import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.Adduct;
019import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.FattyAcid;
020import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.FunctionalGroup;
021import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.Headgroup;
022import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.HeadgroupDecorator;
023import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.KnownFunctionalGroups;
024import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidAdduct;
025import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidException;
026import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidFaBondType;
027import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidLevel;
028import org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidParsingException;
029import java.util.ArrayList;
030import java.util.Map;
031import static java.util.Map.entry;
032
033/**
034 * Event handler implementation for the {@link SwissLipidsParser}.
035 *
036 * @author Dominik Kopczynski
037 * @author Nils Hoffmann
038 */
039public class SwissLipidsParserEventHandler extends LipidBaseParserEventHandler {
040
041    public int dbPosition;
042    public String dbCistrans;
043    public int suffixNumber;
044
045    /**
046     * Create a new {@code SwissLipidsParserEventHandler}.
047     *
048     * @param knownFunctionalGroups the known functional groups
049     */
050    public SwissLipidsParserEventHandler(KnownFunctionalGroups knownFunctionalGroups) {
051        super(knownFunctionalGroups);
052        try {
053            registeredEvents = Map.ofEntries(
054                    entry("lipid_pre_event", this::resetParser),
055                    entry("lipid_post_event", this::buildLipid),
056                    // set adduct events
057                    entry("adduct_info_pre_event", this::newAdduct),
058                    entry("adduct_pre_event", this::addAdduct),
059                    entry("charge_pre_event", this::addCharge),
060                    entry("charge_sign_pre_event", this::addChargeSign),
061                    entry("fa_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
062                    entry("gl_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
063                    entry("gl_molecular_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
064                    entry("mediator_pre_event", this::mediatorEvent),
065                    entry("gl_mono_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
066                    entry("pl_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
067                    entry("pl_three_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
068                    entry("pl_four_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
069                    entry("sl_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
070                    entry("st_species_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
071                    entry("st_sub1_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
072                    entry("st_sub2_hg_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupNameSe),
073                    entry("fa_species_pre_event", this::setSpeciesLevel),
074                    entry("gl_molecular_pre_event", this::setMolecularLevel),
075                    entry("unsorted_fa_separator_pre_event", this::setMolecularLevel),
076                    entry("fa2_unsorted_pre_event", this::setMolecularLevel),
077                    entry("fa3_unsorted_pre_event", this::setMolecularLevel),
078                    entry("fa4_unsorted_pre_event", this::setMolecularLevel),
079                    entry("db_single_position_pre_event", this::setIsomericLevel),
080                    entry("db_single_position_post_event", this::addDbPosition),
081                    entry("db_position_number_pre_event", this::addDbPositionNumber),
082                    entry("cistrans_pre_event", this::addCistrans),
083                    entry("lcb_pre_event", this::newLcb),
084                    entry("lcb_post_event", this::cleanLcb),
085                    entry("fa_pre_event", this::newFa),
086                    entry("fa_post_event", this::appendFa),
087                    entry("ether_pre_event", this::addEther),
088                    entry("hydroxyl_pre_event", this::addHydroxyl),
089                    entry("db_count_pre_event", this::addDoubleBonds),
090                    entry("carbon_pre_event", this::addCarbon),
091                    entry("sl_lcb_species_pre_event", this::setSpeciesLevel),
092                    entry("st_species_fa_post_event", this::setSpeciesFa),
093                    entry("fa_lcb_suffix_type_pre_event", this::addFaLcbSuffixType),
094                    entry("fa_lcb_suffix_number_pre_event", this::addSuffixNumber),
095                    entry("pl_three_post_event", this::setNape)
096            );
097        } catch (Exception e) {
098            throw new LipidParsingException("Cannot initialize LipidMapsParserEventHandler.");
099        }
100    }
101
102    @Override
103    protected void resetParser(TreeNode node) {
104        content = null;
105        level = LipidLevel.FULL_STRUCTURE;
106        adduct = null;
107        headGroup = "";
108        lcb = null;
109        faList.clear();
110        currentFa = null;
111        useHeadGroup = false;
112        dbPosition = 0;
113        dbCistrans = "";
114        headgroupDecorators.clear();
115        suffixNumber = -1;
116    }
117
118    private void setIsomericLevel(TreeNode node) {
119        dbPosition = 0;
120        dbCistrans = "";
121    }
122
123    private void addDbPosition(TreeNode node) {
124        if (currentFa != null) {
125            currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().put(dbPosition, dbCistrans);
126            if (!dbCistrans.equals("E") && !dbCistrans.equals("Z")) {
127                setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
128            }
129        }
130    }
131
132    private void setNape(TreeNode node) {
133        headGroup = "PE-N";
134        HeadgroupDecorator hgd = new HeadgroupDecorator("decorator_acyl", -1, 1, null, true, knownFunctionalGroups);
135        headgroupDecorators.add(hgd);
136        hgd.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("decorator_acyl", new ArrayList<>());
137        hgd.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("decorator_acyl").add(faList.get(faList.size() - 1));
138        faList.remove(faList.size() - 1);
139    }
140
141    private void addDbPositionNumber(TreeNode node) {
142        dbPosition = node.getInt();
143    }
144
145    private void addCistrans(TreeNode node) {
146        dbCistrans = node.getText();
147    }
148
149    private void setHeadGroupName(TreeNode node) {
150        headGroup = node.getText();
151    }
152
153    private void setHeadGroupNameSe(TreeNode node) {
154        headGroup = node.getText().replace("(", " ");
155    }
156
157    private void setSpeciesLevel(TreeNode node) {
158        setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.SPECIES);
159    }
160
161    private void setMolecularLevel(TreeNode node) {
162        setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.MOLECULAR_SPECIES);
163    }
164
165    private void mediatorEvent(TreeNode node) {
166        useHeadGroup = true;
167        headGroup = node.getText();
168    }
169
170    private void newFa(TreeNode node) {
171        currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", knownFunctionalGroups);
172    }
173
174    private void newLcb(TreeNode node) {
175        lcb = new FattyAcid("LCB", knownFunctionalGroups);
176        lcb.setType(LipidFaBondType.LCB_REGULAR);
177        currentFa = lcb;
178        setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
179    }
180
181    private void cleanLcb(TreeNode node) {
182        if (currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().isEmpty() && currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() > 0) {
183            setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.SN_POSITION);
184        }
185        currentFa = null;
186    }
187
188    private void appendFa(TreeNode node) {
189        if (currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() < 0) {
190            throw new LipidException("Double bond count does not match with number of double bond positions");
191        }
192
193        if (currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().isEmpty() && currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() > 0) {
194            setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.SN_POSITION);
195        }
196
197        faList.add(currentFa);
198        currentFa = null;
199    }
200
201    private void buildLipid(TreeNode node) {
202        if (lcb != null) {
203            faList.add(0, lcb);
204        }
205
206        Headgroup headgroup = prepareHeadgroupAndChecks();
207        LipidAdduct lipid = new LipidAdduct(assembleLipid(headgroup), adduct);
208        content = lipid;
209    }
210
211    private void addEther(TreeNode node) {
212        String ether = node.getText();
213        if (ether.equals("O-")) {
214            currentFa.setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.ETHER_PLASMANYL);
215        } else if (ether.equals("P-")) {
216            currentFa.setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.ETHER_PLASMENYL);
217        }
218    }
219
220    private void addHydroxyl(TreeNode node) {
221        String old_hydroxyl = node.getText();
222        int num_h = 0;
223        if (old_hydroxyl.equals("m")) {
224            num_h = 1;
225        } else if (old_hydroxyl.equals("d")) {
226            num_h = 2;
227        } else if (old_hydroxyl.equals("t")) {
228            num_h = 3;
229        }
230
231        if (spRegularLcb()) {
232            num_h -= 1;
233        }
234        FunctionalGroup functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
235        functional_group.setCount(num_h);
236        if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("OH")) {
237            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("OH", new ArrayList<>());
238        }
239        currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group);
240    }
241
242    private void addOneHydroxyl(TreeNode node) {
243        if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("OH") && currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").get(0).getPosition() == -1) {
244            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").get(0).setCount(currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").get(0).getCount() + 1);
245        } else {
246            FunctionalGroup functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
247            if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("OH")) {
248                currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("OH", new ArrayList<>());
249            }
250            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group);
251        }
252    }
253
254    private void addSuffixNumber(TreeNode node) {
255        suffixNumber = node.getInt();
256    }
257
258    private void addFaLcbSuffixType(TreeNode node) {
259        String suffix_type = node.getText();
260        if (suffix_type.equals("me")) {
261            suffix_type = "Me";
262            currentFa.setNumCarbon(currentFa.getNumCarbon() - 1);
263        }
264
265        FunctionalGroup functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get(suffix_type);
266        functional_group.setPosition(suffixNumber);
267        if (functional_group.getPosition() == -1) {
268            setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
269        }
270        if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey(suffix_type)) {
271            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put(suffix_type, new ArrayList<>());
272        }
273        currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(suffix_type).add(functional_group);
274
275        suffixNumber = -1;
276    }
277
278    private void addDoubleBonds(TreeNode node) {
279        currentFa.getDoubleBonds().setNumDoubleBonds(currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() + node.getInt());
280    }
281
282    private void addCarbon(TreeNode node) {
283        currentFa.setNumCarbon(node.getInt());
284    }
285
286    private void setSpeciesFa(TreeNode node) {
287        headGroup += " 27:1";
288        faList.get(faList.size() - 1).setNumCarbon(faList.get(faList.size() - 1).getNumCarbon() - 27);
289        faList.get(faList.size() - 1).getDoubleBonds().setNumDoubleBonds(faList.get(faList.size() - 1).getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() - 1);
290    }
291
292    private void newAdduct(TreeNode node) {
293        adduct = new Adduct("", "");
294    }
295
296    private void addAdduct(TreeNode node) {
297        adduct.setAdductString(node.getText());
298    }
299
300    private void addCharge(TreeNode node) {
301        adduct.setCharge(Integer.valueOf(node.getText()));
302    }
303
304    private void addChargeSign(TreeNode node) {
305        String sign = node.getText();
306        if (sign.equals("+")) {
307            adduct.setChargeSign(1);
308        } else if (sign.equals("-")) {
309            adduct.setChargeSign(-1);
310        }
311    }
312}
